  "title": "Sales Support Executive",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:-</p>\n<p>¨ Provide administrative support to the team leaders / members.</p>\n<p>¨ Quote prices, credit terms and delivery conditions.</p>\n<p>¨ Prepare picking (parts requisition) notes.</p>\n<p>¨ Generate sales invoices / cash memos and delivery orders.</p>\n<p>¨ Attend to customer enquiries and follow-up.</p>\n<p>¨ General clerical duties such as filing etc.</p>\n<p>¨ Perform ad-hoc duties / tasks as required by the Company or instructed by the team leader.</p>\n<p>¨ Perform stock-take duties.</p>\n<p>Requirements:-</p>\n<p>¨ Minimum GCE N/O level</p>\n<p>¨ Proficient in MS Office and PC literate</p>\n<p>¨ Preferably with Admin Experience</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Salary Range: $2,600 to $4,000 (inclusive of incentives)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates can send your resume to hr@kianann.com.sg.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
